{"tid":1481490,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦：抗爭抱「對等武力」原則；但何謂「對等武力」？","createTime":"2019-08-17T17:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T16:09:42.000Z","uid":92479,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"96a5ac14b61e615ce02a1ba2f7e56df1f1ac7f48","tid":1481490,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/022101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F022101.jpg&h=07174065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>根據美國憲法第二修正案</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">只有雙方擁有對等&ldquo;武力&rdquo;先可以互相制衡，亦都提醒政府要&ldquo;恐懼&rdquo;人民。</span><br />\nGovernment of the people, by the people, for the people, shall not perish from the Earth.<br />\nAbraham Lincoln <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%94%B0%E5%A3%AB%E5%A4%9A/%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E8%AD%A6%E6%AC%8A%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88%E6%99%82-5789d0f2ee5b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25A4%259A%2F%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2588%25E6%2599%2582-5789d0f2ee5b&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1DizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=67535e8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%94%B0%E5%A3%AB%E5%A4%9A/%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E8%AD%A6%E6%AC%8A%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88%E6%99%82-5789d0f2ee5b</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20160301_20160301-155559.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20160301_20160301-155559.jpg&h=76ad87d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">早前曾稱抗爭「沒有底線」的梁天琦表示，「無底線」是指抗爭者願意付出的代價沒有底線，但不代表無原則，而原則是採取跟警方對等的武力。楊岳橋則在被問到公民黨為何譴責旺角抗爭者時稱，公民黨是針對暴力，對警察亦一樣譴責，他個人能夠理解抗爭者抗爭的原因。\n\n梁天琦與楊岳橋一同出席D100電台舉辦的選舉論壇，期間梁天琦被主持吳志森問到他近日提到抗爭「沒有底線」，是否代表會暗殺？梁天琦稱，「無底線」並不代表「無原則」，「無底線」的意思只是他們什麼代價都肯付出，但他們仍有底線，就是會對警方採用對等的武力。他指出，示威者不會隨便攻撃警察，乃是受到壓迫，才會反抗。\n\n梁：群眾決定抗爭方式 \n吳志森追問梁，若警察對示威者做成嚴重傷害，他會否向對方施以對等武力；梁天琦則表示，他一直反對社運精英領導，認為要由群眾決定他們抗爭的方式。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但點樣先係對等武力呢？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">黑警就會咁分，遵行一種比對方武力「高一級原則」 (one-up principle)的指引，理由是要達到控制對方的目的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【不合法被殺】六級武力指引 遇反抗、埋身肉搏 學堂都無教箍頸<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>武力指引分六層次</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n據《警察通例》第29章，即「武力與槍械的使用」章節，有六級制的「武力使用層次」，如遇心理威嚇及言語對抗，只是口頭勸喻應對，及可召喚增援；如遇消極抵抗，可溫和拘押，出動2至4人搬移；頑強對抗，則可用上胡椒噴劑；遇暴力攻擊，即現場有毆打，但無意令他人嚴重受傷，可使用屬中級武力的警棍；最高等級，如對方的毆打意圖是令人嚴重受傷、死亡，警察可使用致命武力，亦即是槍械。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/250829/%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E8%A2%AB%E6%AE%BA-%E5%85%AD%E7%B4%9A%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95-%E9%81%87%E5%8F%8D%E6%8A%97-%E5%9F%8B%E8%BA%AB%E8%82%89%E6%90%8F-%E5%AD%B8%E5%A0%82%E9%83%BD%E7%84%A1%E6%95%99%E7%AE%8D%E9%A0%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F250829%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E5%2585%25AD%25E7%25B4%259A%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25BC%2595-%25E9%2581%2587%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%258A%2597-%25E5%259F%258B%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%2582%2589%25E6%2590%258F-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%2583%25BD%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%25AE%258D%25E9%25A0%25B8&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1DizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=6fba8fa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/250829/%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E8%A2%AB%E6%AE%BA-%E5%85%AD%E7%B4%9A%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95-%E9%81%87%E5%8F%8D%E6%8A%97-%E5%9F%8B%E8%BA%AB%E8%82%89%E6%90%8F-%E5%AD%B8%E5%A0%82%E9%83%BD%E7%84%A1%E6%95%99%E7%AE%8D%E9%A0%B8</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://jmc.hksyu.edu/ourvoice/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/2014-12-30-02.17.04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjmc.hksyu.edu%2Fourvoice%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F12%2F2014-12-30-02.17.04.jpg&h=a7d89002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n對於抗爭者黎講武器防具只有遮/丫叉/營火玻璃樽/魚絲/浮板/豬咀/眼罩，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以上呢啲野極其量只能夠應付胡椒噴霧/警棍。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">當大家遇上「胡椒噴霧/警棍」，係必須撤離現場，因為經評估之後根本無得打，除非你升級到做大型火魔法師，否則不應硬碰！<br />\n如果要撤退，請於哨兵發現敵方包圍網完成２５％前決定，否則已無退路！<br />\n請提高危機意識，及不要背向敵人！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">請各位當下認清實況決定打定走<br />\n最後希望各位武運昌隆！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20160331/large/31ls2p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160331%2Flarge%2F31ls2p1.jpg&h=6a1b36cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f3c46a7c7b5d6721552e4032cb034703ca10d5","tid":1481490,"uid":92479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/yuen-01_OwdeV_600x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fyuen-01_OwdeV_600x0.png&h=d4904421&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"956df88db9f5f8c74ed5d249946e53866c1c7073","tid":1481490,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/44023863_1882232731861421_1119453938320408576_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQkKY25jGmaK0fp0AfZasHu5FU8ppELUzKeKRH